    <briefdescription>
<para>Element-by-element subtraction of two vectors. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><preformatted>
    dst[n] = src_a[n] - src_b[n],   0 &lt;= n &lt; block_size.
</preformatted> There are separate functions for floating-point, Q7, Q15, and Q31 data types. </para>
